\c 51
\s Kudzoswa kwaIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Teererai kwandiri, imwi munotsvakisisa kururama, imwi munotsvaka Jehovha; tarirai kudombo pamafomborwa, nekugomba remugodhi pamakacherwa.
\v 2 Tarairai kuna Abhurahama baba venyu, naSara wakakuberekai; nokuti ndakamudana ari ega ndikamuropafadza ndokumuwanza.
\v 3 Nokuti Jehovha achanyaradza Ziyoni; achanyaradza matongo aro ese, uye achaita renje raro rive seEdheni, negwenga raro rive sebindi raJehovha; mufaro nekupembera zvichawanikwamo, kuvonga, neinzwi rekuimba.
\p
\v 4 Teererai kwandiri, vanhu vangu; uye ipai nzeve kwandiri imwi rudzi, nokuti murairo uchabuda mandiri. uye ndichazorodza mutongo wangu uve chiedza chevanhu.
\v 5 Kururama kwangu kuri pedo, ruponeso rwangu rwabuda, uye maoko angu achatonga vanhu; zviwi zvichandimirira, uye zvichavimba neruoko rwangu.
\v 6 Simudzirai meso enyu kumatenga, uye mutarisise nyika pasi; nokuti matenga achanyangarika seutsi, nenyika ichasakara senguvo; vageremo vachafa saizvozvo; asi ruponeso rwangu ruchava nekusingaperi, uye kururama kwangu hakungaparadzwi.
\p
\v 7 Teererai kwandiri, imwi munoziva kururama, rudzi mumoyo marwo mune murairo wangu; musatya kuzvidza kwevanhu, kana kuvhunduswa nezvituko zvavo.
\v 8 Nokuti chipfukuto chichavadya senguvo, nehonye ivadye semvere; asi kururama kwangu kuchavapo nekusingaperi, neruponeso rwangu kusvika kumazera nemazera.
\p
\v 9 Muka, muka, zvifukidze simba, iwe ruoko rwaJehovha; muka s\add epa\add*mazuva ekare, se\add pa\add*zera renguva dzekarekare. Hausi iwe here wakagura Rahabhi, mukakuvadza bukanana here?
\v 10 Hamusi imwi here mapapwisa gungwa, mvura zvinji yeudziku ukuru, makaita udziku hwegungwa huve nzira yevakadzikunurwa kuti vapfuure \add nayo\add*?
\v 11 Naizvozvo vakadzikunurwa vaJehovha vachadzoka, uye vachauya nekuimba kuZiyoni, nemufaro wekusingaperi pamusoro pemusoro wavo. Vachawana mufaro nekupembera. Kusuwa nekuchema zvichatiza.
\p
\v 12 Ini, i\add ye\add*ni, ndini ndinokunyaradzai; ndiwe ani kuti utye munhu anozofa, kana mwanakomana wemunhu, achaitwa uswa;
\v 13 uye wakakanganwa Jehovha muiti wako, iye wakatatamura matenga, nekuteya nheyo dzenyika; unoramba uchitya mazuva ese nekuda kwehasha dzemumanikidzi, sezvinonzi akazvipira kuparara here? Zvino hasha dzemumanikidzi dziripi?
\v 14 Musungwa wakatapwa anokurumidza kuti asunungurwe, uye kuti asafira mugomba, kana kuti kudya kwake kusashaikwa.
\v 15 Nokuti ndini Jehovha Mwari wako anomutsa gungwa, kuti mafungu aro atinhire; Jehovha wehondo ndiro zita rake.
\v 16 Zvino ndakaisa mashoko angu mumuromo mako, uye ndikakufukidza mumumvuri weruoko rwangu, kuti ndidzvare matenga, nekuteya nheyo dzenyika, uye nditi kuZiyoni: Muri vanhu vangu.
\p
\v 17 Muka, muka, simuka, Jerusarema, iwe wakanwa kubva paruoko rwaJehovha mukombe wekutsamwa kwake; wakanwa manzete emukombe wese wekudederesa, ukaakweva.
\v 18 Hakuna pakati pavanakomana vake vese vaakabereka angamutungamirira, hakuna angamubata noruoko pakati pavanakomana vese vaakarera.
\v 19 Zvinhu izvi zviviri zvakuwira; ndianiko achakunzwira tsitsi? Kusiiwa nokuparadzwa, nenzara nomunondo; ndingakunyaradza sei?
\v 20 Vanakomana vako vaziya, varere pamigumo yenzira dzomumusha, senzombe yesango yabatwa mumambure; vazadzwa nokutsamwa kwaJehovha nokutuka kwaMwari wako.
\p
\v 21 Naizvozvo zvino chinzwa chinhu ichi, iwe unotambudzika, wakabatwa, asi kwete newaini.
\v 22 Ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe wako Jehovha, naMwari wako, unoreverera vanhu vake: Tarirai, ndakabvisa muruoko rwako mukombe wokudzedzeresa, iwo manzete emukombe wokutsamwa kwangu, haungazoamwizve.
\v 23 Asi ndichauisa muruoko rwavanokutambudza, ivo vakati kumweya wako: Kotama, kuti tipfuure napamusoro; iwe ukaita musana wako sapasi, senzira yomumusha yavanopfuura.
